CT of serous cystadenoma of the pancreas and mimicking masses. The purpose of this article is to illustrate the varied CT appearances of serous cystadenoma of the pancreas and of masses that mimic serous cystadenoma.Serous cystadenomas of the pancreas have a wide range of CT findings. Familiarity with the varied CT appearances and awareness of the diagnostic limitations of CT are important for accurate diagnosis and management of serous cystadenoma of the pancreas.